		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/07/rt-breaking-set-interview-about-spies-abby-martin.html" title="Permalink to RT Breaking the Set — interview about spies with Abby Martin" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> Breaking the Set — interview about spies with Abby Martin</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/07/rt-breaking-set-interview-about-spies-abby-martin.html" title="20:27" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-07-23T20:27:05+00:00" pubdate>July 23, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/07/rt-breaking-set-interview-about-spies-abby-martin.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here’s my inter­view from yes­ter­day on <span class="caps">RT</span>’s excel­lent <a href="http://rt.com/shows/breaking-set-summary/">Break­ing the Set</a> show with host, Abby Mar­tin.  We dis­cussed all things spy, sur­veil­lance, Snowden, over­sight, and pri­vacy.  A fun and lively inter­view!  Thanks, Abby.<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/101496843" width="500" height="281" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/101496843">Brit­ish Spies Con­trolling the Past, Present and Future — Inter­view with Annie Machon</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
