	<article id="post-3793" class="post-3793 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-accountability category-civil-liberties category-cryptoparty category-intelligence category-machon category-national-security category-nsa category-open-source category-privacy-2 category-rttv category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-tv category-whistleblowers tag-accountability-2 tag-annie-machon tag-edward-snowden tag-intelligence-2 tag-nsa tag-open-source-2 tag-pgp tag-privacy tag-spies-2 tag-surveillance-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/rt-interview-anniversary-edward-snowden.html" title="Permalink to RT Interview — the anniversary of Edward Snowden" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> Interview — the anniversary of Edward Snowden</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/rt-interview-anniversary-edward-snowden.html" title="16:58" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-06-10T16:58:30+00:00" pubdate>June 10, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/rt-interview-anniversary-edward-snowden.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is an inter­view I did on 5<sup>th</sup> June, the anniversary of the start of Edward Snowden’s dis­clos­ures about the global sur­veil­lance infra­struc­ture that is being built.</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/rt_int_snowden.jpg" alt="rt_int_snowden" width="707" height="396" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3828" data-source="vimeo" data-id="97758987" /></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/97758987"><span class="caps">RT</span> inter­view on Snowden <span class="amp">&amp;</span> digital pri­vacy</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/06/rt-interview-anniversary-edward-snowden.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/accountability" title="View all posts in Accountability" rel="category tag">Accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/civil-liberties" title="View all posts in Civil Liberties" rel="category tag">Civil Liberties</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/cryptoparty" title="View all posts in Cryptoparty" rel="category tag">Cryptoparty</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/machon" title="View all posts in Machon" rel="category tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/national-security" title="View all posts in National security" rel="category tag">National security</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/nsa" title="View all posts in NSA" rel="category tag">NSA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/open-source" title="View all posts in Open source" rel="category tag">Open source</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/privacy-2" title="View all posts in Privacy" rel="category tag">Privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/rttv" title="View all posts in RTTV" rel="category tag">RTTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/snowden" title="View all posts in Snowden" rel="category tag">Snowden</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/surveillance" title="View all posts in Surveillance" rel="category tag">Surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/tv" title="View all posts in TV" rel="category tag">TV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/whistleblowers" title="View all posts in Whistleblowers" rel="category tag">Whistleblowers</a>			</span>
