							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/accountability-2" rel="tag">accountability</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/courage-foundation" rel="tag">Courage Foundation</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/law-2" rel="tag">law</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/privacy" rel="tag">privacy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/whistleblowers-2" rel="tag">whistleblowers</a>			</span>
						
